nodes.text: "Crane" was a male Clone Commander who, in a Force vision experienced by Dooku, served under Jedi Master Jor Aerith during the Clone Wars. During a battle, Crane executed Order 66 and shot the Jedi Master.
Crane first appeared in the audiobook Dooku: Jedi Lost, written by Cavan Scott and published in 2019.
